_:N96d35c9ac69b460a835fb0fe1ca3fe27 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>John has been an integral part of our Geological Disposal Facility (GDF) programme since 2016. Before joining the programme, John was in the Royal Navy with a 30 year nuclear engineering career as a submariner.  In his last Defence role he was the UK’s Director of Nuclear Propulsion; responsible for all aspects of designing, delivering and supporting a fleet of submarine reactor plants.</p>\n" .
